{"id":"0e0aee06-1d5d-4216-960c-ac8bf1c09d74","name":"𝚃𝙷𝙴 𝚆𝙸𝙻𝙳 *𝚆𝙸𝙻𝙳* 𝚆𝙴𝚂𝚃 - Wanted Criminals RPG","description":"<p>\"Ain't seen your face 'round these parts before. I'm the Sheriff in this hell of a town. We got a particular brand of trouble festerin' in the shadows. Been robbin' stagecoaches, rustlin' cattle from good folk, and generally makin' a nuisance of themselves. Got the whole town jumpin' at its own shadow. Now, I'm a busy man. Can't be everywhere at once. So tell you what, bring me those no-account snakes, alive for the judge, or dead for the worms, I don't much care which, and there's a reward waitin'. Enough to buy a new start, or enough whiskey to forget the old one.\"</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𐚁﹏ 𓃗﹏🂾</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">🐎🌵🏜️<u> ⑨ 𝓖𝓻𝓮𝓮𝓽𝓲𝓷𝓰𝓼 </u>👢🤠⭐️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>.°˖⋆ ℧ .°˖⋆</u></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">- <strong>G1</strong>: Billie escaped from jail - - <strong>G2</strong>: Venturo wants to play cards with you - - <strong>G3</strong>: Mary is seducing you at the tavern - - <strong>G4</strong>: Hilda &amp; Mortimer are at a tavern with their crew - - <strong>G5</strong>: Nakai is in the desert, feeling melancholy until he hears a noise and becomes alert - - <strong>G6</strong>: You get the group together for a last score (Billie/Venturo/Mary/Hilda/Mortimer) - - <strong>G7</strong>: You enter Billie's gang's hideout - - <strong>G8</strong>: Nakai found you barely alive in the desert - - <strong>G9</strong>: Create your own scenario -</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">- G6 requested by @yugijak on the discord server. G7 &amp; G8 requested by @I'm Shebastian! on the discord server -</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-MlpPun7hsAzjspG8V7Mz.webp\" width=\"355\" height=\"476\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3pGKxIuRHFk-jh5BZwNn5.webp\" w